title: NYC Campaign Finance Board database schema and documentation

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the New York Freedom of Information Law, I hereby request the following records:

Copies of all documentation, data dictionaries, schema declarations and other information materials about the campaign finance reporting database maintained by your agency.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Ben Welsh

title: Grand Central Madison digital art by Yayoi Kusama

communications.subject: New York Freedom of Information Law Request: Grand Central Madison digital art by Yayoi Kusama
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the New York Freedom of Information Law, I hereby request the following records:

All digital art files prepared by Yayoi Kusama for the creation of mosaics at Grand Central Madison. I ask that the files be released in the same format they were provided by the artist, be it PDF, Adobe Illustrator or some other digital vector format.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Ben Welsh

title: Grand Central Madison design guides and standards manuals

communications.subject: New York Freedom of Information Law Request: Grand Central Madison design guides and standards manuals
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the New York Freedom of Information Law, I hereby request the following records:

All design guides and standards manuals prepared for the launch of Grand Central Madison. I am asking for the release of all materials prepared to inform and outline the presentation of the new station's branding, marketing and advertisement.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Ben Welsh
